= How this game works

**This story plays like a chat.**

• Click an answer to continue. 

• New content appears below the bar at the bottom. 

• If you can’t see the newest message, scroll. 

= Sidebars

**Use the buttons in the top bar to open the side panels:**

• Progress (map icon): shows what you’ve done so far.

• Info (info icon): shows helpful context and lets you toggle theme and save/load.

